                        <p class="pt-xl-3 pt-md-0 pt-2">In 2019, Mr. Kailash Chand embarked on the journey of Shine Airways, commencing it
                            under the banner of COSWAY Enterprise. With no collaborators, he took charge of the marketing
                            crusade, adorning nocturnal streets with posters while tending to daylong calls himself. His
                            relentless dedication drove the airline's initial strides, forging a path marked by individual commitment.
                        </p>

                        <p>From the moment you step on board, you are welcomed with warm
